##--- How to type tilde?
* Alt + N

##--- How to cd a directory with a name containing spaces?
* cd Library/Application\ Support/

##— Where are QuickTime Player’s tmp files stored?

    Library/Containers/com.apple.QuickTimePlayerX/Data/Library/Autosave Information/Unsaved QuickTime Player Document.qtpxcomposition/Screen\ Audio Recording.m4a

##--- copy/move a file from a directory to another
* cp ~/Downloads/R.plist ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextWrangler/Language\ Modules/

## --- Snipping Tool
* cmd + shift + 4

## --- Parallels: remove virtual machine
* cd ~/Documents/Parallels/
* rm -rf Ubuntu\ Linux\ 14.04\ Desktop.pvm/

## --- to check java versions in Mac
* cd /System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/
* ls
* To change to any versions:
> sudo ln -fhsv 1.6 CurrentJDK
> java -versions
## --- look into environment variables in the path
> echo $PATH
> set a new path: http://coolestguidesontheplanet.com/add-shell-path-osx/

## --- change directory to flash drive
> cd /Volumes/NIGATWA

## --- open your file (.txt) from the Terminal
> open myfile.txt

